{
  "info": {
    "name": "移动办公后台接口",
    "description": "Mobile Office App 后端 API 测试集合\n\n使用步骤：\n1. 先运行「用户登录」接口获取 token\n2. Collection 变量会自动保存 token，后续接口通过 Authorization: Bearer <token> 携带\n3. 依次测试其他接口",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3002/api/mobile_officing",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3002/admin/file",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "roomId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "一、用户模块",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. 用户登录",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"loginname\": \"17704051019\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "login"]
            },
            "description": "登录获取token\n\n请求体：\n- loginname: 登录账号（手机号）\n- password: 登录密码\n\n响应成功示例：\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"登录成功\",\n  \"data\": { \"token\": \"eyJhbG...\" }\n}\n```"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.code === 200 && jsonData.data && jsonData.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.data.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token saved to collection variables');",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('登录成功', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.code).to.equal(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('token');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "2. 获取用户信息",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}",
                "description": "登录时获取的JWT Token，格式：Bearer <token>"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/info",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "info"]
            },
            "description": "获取当前登录用户的详细信息\n\n需要在请求头中携带 Authorization: Bearer <token>\n\n响应成功示例：\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"获取成功\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"userid\": \"user_b7d8955c-...\",\n    \"username\": \"张三\",\n    \"loginname\": \"17704051019\",\n    \"tel\": \"17704051019\",\n    \"nickname\": \"张三\",\n    \"sex\": 1,\n    \"score\": 100\n  }\n}\n```"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('获取用户信息成功', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.code).to.equal(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('userid');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('nickname');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "3. 获取短信验证码",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/smscode?phone=13800138000",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "smscode"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "phone",
                  "value": "13800138000",
                  "description": "手机号码"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "获取短信验证码（当前为模拟实现，验证码直接返回在响应中）\n\n请求参数：\n- phone: 手机号码\n\n响应成功示例：\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"验证码发送成功\",\n  \"data\": { \"code\": \"382916\" }\n}\n```"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('获取验证码成功', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.code).to.equal(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('code');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.data.code).to.have.lengthOf(6);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "4. 更换手机号",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"13800138000\",\n  \"code\": \"382916\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/changePhone",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "changePhone"]
            },
            "description": "更换绑定的手机号码\n\n需要先通过「获取短信验证码」接口获取验证码\n\n请求体：\n- phone: 新手机号\n- code: 短信验证码\n\n响应成功示例：\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"手机号修改成功\"\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. 修改密码",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"oldPassword\": \"123456\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"654321\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/changePassword",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "changePassword"]
            },
            "description": "修改登录密码\n\n请求体：\n- oldPassword: 原密码\n- newPassword: 新密码（6-16位）\n\n响应成功示例：\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"密码修改成功\"\n}\n```\n\n注意：修改密码成功后需要重新登录"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6. 忘记密码（重置密码）",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"17704051019\",\n  \"code\": \"382916\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"654321\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/resetPassword",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "resetPassword"]
            },
            "description": "忘记密码 - 通过手机验证码重置密码（无需登录）\n\n调用流程：\n1. 先调用「获取短信验证码」接口获取验证码\n2. 提交手机号、验证码和新密码\n\n请求体：\n- phone: 注册手机号\n- code: 短信验证码\n- newPassword: 新密码\n\n响应成功示例：\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"密码重置成功\"\n}\n```\n\n错误响应：\n- 验证码错误或已过期: { \"code\": 400, \"message\": \"验证码错误或已过期\" }\n- 手机号未注册: { \"code\": 400, \"message\": \"该手机号未注册\" }"
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('密码重置成功', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.code).to.equal(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.message).to.equal('密码重置成功');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
